text: Jochen Mehrdorf (born 14 July 1940) is a German equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of West Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Braunschweig
